Class SWCFileScopeProvider.SWCFileScope

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.scopes.ASScopeBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IASScope, IFileScope
    Enclosing class:
    SWCFileScopeProvider

    public static final class SWCFileScopeProvider.SWCFileScope
extends ASFileScope
    This class is able to resolve the source file path of a given QName defined in a SWC library, if the source directory is set for that SWC library.

      • getContainingSourcePath

        public String getContainingSourcePath(String qName,
                             ICompilerProject project)
        Description copied from class: ASFileScope
        Resolve the source file path of the given definition QName. The QName must be defined within this file scope.

        If this ASFileScope comes from an ActionScript file, return the ActionScript file path. File scopes coming from ABC or SWC files will override this method to locate their source file path.

        Overrides:
        getContainingSourcePath in class ASFileScope
        Parameters:
        qName - QName of a definition
        project - resolve the source path within this project
        Returns:
        Source file path of this ASFileScope.
